Lulutho Sokupe (8) was last seen with his grandmother last Wednesday. CAPE TOWN - The search for a missing Kuils River boy has entered its sixth day.Lulutho Sokupe (8) was last seen with his grandmother last Wednesday at the Vrygrond informal settlement. He was wearing blue pants and had a pink bike with him.Dessie Rechner of missing children organisation the Pink Ladies. Please contact the SAPS Kuils River Sergeant Parring on 021 900 2845 or the Pink Ladies on 072 2147439. (Edited by Neo Koza)